# Image Data Augmentation and Image Classification

Spring Internship Program 2026  
IDEAS-TIH, Indian Statistical Institute, Kolkata  

## 📌 Project Overview
This project demonstrates:

- Image loading using OpenCV
- Grayscale conversion
- Image transformation (shift, resize, rotate)
- Dataset download and extraction
- PyTorch ImageFolder dataset creation
- DataLoader creation
- Data augmentation pipeline
- Batch visualization

## 🛠 Technologies Used
- Python
- OpenCV
- NumPy
- PyTorch
- Torchvision
- Matplotlib

## 📂 Dataset
Cat and Dog dataset from Udacity:
https://s3.amazonaws.com/content.udacity-data.com/nd089/Cat_Dog_data.zip

